biz.aduna.map.cluster
Class DefaultCluster

java.lang.Object
  biz.aduna.map.cluster.DefaultCluster
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cluster
public class DefaultCluster
extends java.lang.Object
implements Cluster

DefaultCluster provides a complete implementation of Cluster. It internally uses a HashSet for registering the Classification's Objects, which for most purposes should be sufficient.
